scripts.build:babel: rm -rf dist/*; mkdir -p dist; babel src/*.js -d dist
scripts.build:babel:index: rm -rf dist/*; mkdir -p dist; babel src/index.js --out-file dist/index.js
scripts.build:babel:auto-bind: rm -rf dist/*; mkdir -p dist/auto-bind ; babel node_modules/auto-bind/*.js -d dist/auto-bind
scripts.build:webpack:prod: rm -rf dist/*; mkdir -p dist; webpack --mode production && es-check es5 dist/main.js
